Rel(\frac{x_{A}}{y_{A}})=\frac{Rel(x_{A})-Rel(y_{A})}{1-Rel(y_{A})}
\approx Rel(x_{A})-Rel(y_{A})
y_{A}
Rel(x_{A})=\frac{x_{T}-x_{A}}{x_{T}}
x_{A}=x_{T}(1-e_{x})
e_{x}
e_X = (x_T- x_A)/x_T
x_A = x_T (1-e_X)
x_T
x_A
e_X
z_A=\frac{x_A}{y_A}=\frac{x_T(1-e_X)}{y_T(1-e_Y)} = z_T \frac{1-e_X}{1-e_Y} \approx z_T (1-e_X)(1+e_Y) \approx z_T (1 - e_X + e_Y)
e_Y \ll 1
 e_Z= e_X + e_Y
z_A = z_T \frac{1-e_X}{1-e_Y} = z_T (1 - e_Z) \implies e_Z = 1 - \frac{1-e_X}{1-e_Y} = \frac{e_X - e_Y}{1-e_Y}
